 600-900 ml","guid":"KOGEbHWFQSCfo4SiJlnfHA","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"Noche moderada 900-1200 ml","guid":"jWqd3UMhT7O3B5Y90xOqLA","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"Supernoche grave >1200 ml","guid":"au3yR2j3ROWJd3Ry3NQZ4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"50","text":"SONDA VESICAL","guid":"lcIOyTWaSyGxF2sOwU8Q7Q","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Indicación: dermatitis, UPP, retención urinaria","guid":"II0uv1lCRjWKWu3pKt85QA","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"Riesgos: ITU, uretritis, hematuria","guid":"mBKo7HEdQ66gE6CPqLmUwQ","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Bolsa SIEMPRE bajo nivel vejiga","guid":"l96BdlrRRfGLuQbY_mLlmA","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"Retirar cuanto antes","guid":"jClNgsWCT8uppYzSEfLNmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"50","text":"COLECTOR PENEANO","guid":"rmUu8vWbRRG1fUpMlaNn-w","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Cambio DIARIO → prevenir ITU","guid":"8vJZnYvjQ-S5q5V-qee1Fw","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"Proteger piel del pene","guid":"H-mPx2zAToGlvoAeJDqSyw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"0","text":"ÚLCERAS POR PRESIÓN (UPP)","guid":"-xtm9nXkQbi-4z5ECwit8w","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Definición → lesión isquémica piel/TCS/músculo por presión mantenida","guid":"hzc5pYcpSueV33PfWQv3PA","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"FISIOPATOLOGÍA (4 fuerzas)","guid":"fVQa-32WT069v4Mr7y1Z9Q","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"PRESIÓN → oclusión capilar >32 mmHg → isquemia","guid":"igQ20LiPRRCf_ZO-Zj4pfQ","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"CIZALLA → arrastre (cabecera >30°)","guid":"D_WmIVKHQQq2aa8yBnzAcQ","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"FRICCIÓN → roce tangencial","guid":"9Jfm4jVzTMC8RBu2UWhDAw","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"HUMEDAD → maceración (sudor, orina, heces)","guid":"r2DFYT7iQrCRQCqpMvcXpg","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"98","text":"LOCALIZACIONES","guid":"SJqjJ2M-TYGko2efnBqegg","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"Decúbito DORSAL → sacro (MÁS FRECUENTE), talones, occipucio, omóplatos, codos","guid":"23pCq3_0SlyN4IOtwGrgCg","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"Decúbito LATERAL → trocánter, maléolo, acromion, oreja","guid":"CYN74Dh0TbOZhtE6chau6w","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"Decúbito PRONO → mejilla, acromion, mamas, genitales, rodillas","guid":"spDVyWOyQVOOSoW_9gd09Q","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"SEDESTACIÓN → isquion, sacro, talón","guid":"47ETwmITT8-SNiCjR03uUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"98","text":"CLASIFICACIÓN NPUAP","guid":"fIN8vzNoQkG3onxM0F7Bpg","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Categoría I → eritema NO blanqueable piel intacta","guid":"EAv8WCSsT52b5PWKe49o7A","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"Categoría II → pérdida parcial dermis, flictena","guid":"myOUowvcS6O8v5uqmMhr_A","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"110","text":"Categoría III → pérdida total piel, grasa visible","guid":"WvBXUHjyQFC_j1HmYU7u5Q","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"110","text":"Categoría IV → pérdida total tejidos + hueso/tendón","guid":"MHK-gbiGS421slxfUB2ZoA","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"110","text":"No clasificable → cubierta esfacelo/escara","guid":"U3GZVbVITsWgu1JfA1T8AA","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"110","text":"Lesión tejidos profundos (LTP) → piel intacta púrpura","guid":"gA1ixfRQT2SPlcFERz6HVA","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"98","text":"ESCALAS DE RIESGO","guid":"m6BAvNaWT0KjQZ8zG8Mvow","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"BRADEN (6 ítems, 6-23 pts) → ≤16 riesgo","guid":"PUtjL_8BRpmVcTRw50C0qw","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Percepción sensorial, humedad, actividad, movilidad, nutrición, fricción/cizalla","guid":"ckTbJDx1R_WfsJ_Y6pMk6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"NORTON (5 ítems, 5-20 pts) → ≤14 ries